{"tid":1701444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［技巧］防衛研究-美軍近戰技巧","createTime":"2019-11-09T05:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T11:01:54.000Z","uid":328502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad3c9e9523601e841c9445bdf471bb1d6e70c08","tid":1701444,"uid":328502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:20:42.000Z","msg":"首先,因為P牌出post, 應該會好快沈<br />\n但我覺得以下既野係對前線及神獸好大作用,所以希望大家推到既都幫手推<br />\n<br />\n今日想同大家研究吓俾人打既防守方法<br />\n下面條LINK係 U.S. Marine Corps Close Combat E-Book, 即係美軍既近戰技術書仔<br />\n書仔講左好多人類身體既攻擊弱點,所以對於近戰<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">防衛</span></strong>係十分有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道人地點樣<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">攻擊</span></strong>,大家先知點樣去<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">防衛</span></strong>.<br />\n<br />\n因為全本都係英文,我靜係睇左圖,如果兄弟英文好既可以詳解俾大家聽.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://index-of.co.uk/Tutorials-2/MCRP%203-02B%20Close%20Combat.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Findex-of.co.uk%2FTutorials-2%2FMCRP%25203-02B%2520Close%2520Combat.pdf&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOAfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=7567b6fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://index-of.co.uk/Tutorials-2/MCRP%203-02B%20Close%20Combat.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nP.10 - 點用手部位去攻擊 (小心人地隻手)<br />\nP.11 - 人類身體弱點 (唔好俾人打到呢d位)<br />\nP.44 - 用棍 (防衛)<br />\nP.53 - 開始講無武器 (其實人既身體有d部位係天生既武器例如 踭/膝)<br />\nP.72 - 開始講既野大家唔好學, OK?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一本差唔多<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bits.de/NRANEU/others/amd-us-archive/FM%2021-150%2892%29.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bits.de%2FNRANEU%2Fothers%2Famd-us-archive%2FFM%252021-150%252892%2529.pdf&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOAfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=4df8e203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bits.de/NRANEU/others/amd-us-archive/FM%2021-150%2892%29.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nP.67 - VITAL TARGETS 人身體既重要目標 (要小心保護自己)<br />\nP.81 - 呢個位好重要,被重激係會有一兩秒唔知做緊乜<br />\nP.83 - 成個肋骨藍最弱既位置<br />\nP.92 - 93 連續動作唔洗講<br />\n扯衫領係好利害既招數,記得小心防範<br />\n記得學好點防衛唔係學黎<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">攻擊</span></strong>,知道未!"},{"pid":"aa909ff422981d6a6e50081efedc27715c7d2691","tid":1701444,"uid":328502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"P牌自推"},{"pid":"a5871fb9243acd9833dc799cfab7a698907cd585","tid":1701444,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"報泰拳班實際好多"},{"pid":"9d85749f61d52617d8f3920600ae17f4153e170e","tid":1701444,"uid":328502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5871fb9243acd9833dc799cfab7a698907cd585","tid":1701444,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"報泰拳班實際好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:26:32.000Z","msg":"未報到前都睇吓<br />\n幫手推下"},{"pid":"cc2372f37345d1f6d22fc108712e24eccbf8891c","tid":1701444,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T08:08:51.000Z","msg":"其實摔交係咪仲好用呢？以近身黎講"},{"pid":"f4297ef6600a037c2fac5bf7546511b0448ef7f9","tid":1701444,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ad3c9e9523601e841c9445bdf471bb1d6e70c08","tid":1701444,"uid":328502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:20:42.000Z","msg":"首先,因為P牌出post, 應該會好快沈<br />\n但我覺得以下既野係對前線及神獸好大作用,所以希望大家推到既都幫手推<br />\n<br />\n今日想同大家研究吓俾人打既防守方法<br />\n下面條LINK係 U.S. Marine Corps Close Combat E-Book, 即係美軍既近戰技術書仔<br />\n書仔講左好多人類身體既攻擊弱點,所以對於近戰<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">防衛</span></strong>係十分有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道人地點樣<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">攻擊</span></strong>,大家先知點樣去<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">防衛</span></strong>.<br />\n<br />\n因為全本都係英文,我靜係睇左圖,如果兄弟英文好既可以詳解俾大家聽.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://index-of.co.uk/Tutorials-2/MCRP%203-02B%20Close%20Combat.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Findex-of.co.u